  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>The traditional Hotel Holiday Debili is perfectly placed if you want quick access to the slopes with one of the main lifts just 100 metres away. Good home cooking will keep you fuelled each day. The heated boot room will ensure your gear is dry and warm and, when you get back from a great day on the mountain, you can relax in the hotel's sauna.</p>]]></listingDescription>
