  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Twin Rooms </strong>sleep up to three people (extra bed is a single bed) and have a balcony, TV, safe, bath with overhead shower and hairdryer. Rooms can be made up with double or twin beds.</p>
<p><strong>Family Rooms </strong>sleep up to four people (extra beds single beds) and are located on the fifth floor without a balcony. They are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Single Rooms </strong>are also available but do not have a balcony.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
